                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d58">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.00/4049: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                        to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-03-10T22:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 10, 1919, 10 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received March 10, 9:10 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1099. My 893, February 24th, 10 p.m. Telegram from <persName corresp="#p_BWC1"
                        >Bullitt</persName> states he expects to reach Petrograd 9th instant. He
                    adds: “I have reason to feel certain that I shall have definite propositions
                    from the Soviet Government to transmit within a week or ten days.” To avoid any
                    misapprehension I handed brief memorandum to <persName corresp="#p_BAJ1"
                        >Balfour</persName> and <persName corresp="#p_PS1">Pichon</persName> this
                    afternoon informing them that <persName corresp="#p_BWC1">Bullitt</persName> is
                    proceeding to Petrograd for information purposes solely.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Am</hi>[<hi rend="smallcaps">erican</hi>] <hi
                        rend="smallcaps">Mission</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
